{{documentation}}

== Purpose ==
This template provides the production version of the template.

== Usage ==
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">
{{TemplateName
 | parameter1 =
 | parameter2 =
}}
</syntaxhighlight>

== Parameters ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Parameter
! Required
! Description
|-
| parameter1
| Yes
| Primary parameter.
|-
| parameter2
| No
| Optional parameter.
|}

== Examples ==
=== Basic ===
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">
{{TemplateName|parameter1=value}}
</syntaxhighlight>

=== Advanced ===
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">
{{TemplateName
 | parameter1 = value
 | parameter2 = example
}}
</syntaxhighlight>

